E%D9%84%D9%8E"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be effaced, to be obliterated, to be obscure, to be unapparent, to be imperceptible; to become effaced, to become obliterated, to become obscure, to become unapparent, to become imperceptible"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be soft, to be smooth; to become soft, to become smooth"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"redundancy of hair, plush, fluff, fuzz, nap"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"fimbriae"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"fringes, fimbriae"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"languid, supine"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n11536","headword_ar":"خَمَلَ","root":"xml","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xumuwlN","text_ar":"خُمُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a place of alighting or abode, Msb, TA, and a tattooing, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, effaced,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"obliterated;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and imperceptible,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unapparent."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  And hence, (Msb,) said of a man, aor. and inf. n. as above,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, obscure, unnoted, reputeless,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of no reputation:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb:) [and] said of a man's reputation ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ikoruhu","text_ar":"ذِكْرُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", JK, K, and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sawotuhu","text_ar":"صَوْتُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", K), aor. as above, (JK,) and so the inf. n., (JK, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, obscure."},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, K.) Some mention also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xamula","text_ar":"خَمُلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"page_break","n":813},{"kind":"text","text":"inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xamaAlapN","text_ar":"خَمَالَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and this inf. n. occurs in a description of the Prophet; but it is only for the purpose of assimilation to its contr."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nabaAhapN","text_ar":"نَبَاهَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b3-  [It is app. also said of speech, meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, low, soft,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gentle:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAmilN","text_ar":"خَامِلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xumila","text_ar":"خُمِلَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man, and a beast, K, a horse, a sheep or goat, and a camel, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"had,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was affected with, the malady termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xumaAl","text_ar":"خُمَال"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.)"}],"source_refs":["Msb","S","JK","K"]}]}}